Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Erika, you can do it! Good luck! Erika! Go for it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Erika...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think a fallen bastard like you can defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even in a situation like this, running is so much fun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk big but l guess it was all bluff!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l already told you. You can't defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall return to the world of light, where we came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But seems like you've fallen too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have done everything to open the gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''The one who plants the seeds will harvest its crop,'' eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this, a reward for working so hard? How considerate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fine. Show me what you got.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}l...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How could l have said such a thing to Akino...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}lt's my fault that Akino...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akino!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erika.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.99,0:22:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akino, l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l had no idea how you were feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.47,0:22:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf l only stopped and thought about it, l would have known!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was only thinking about myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.27,0:22:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's fine. We've known each other for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l knew you weren't being malicious... but l was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.82,0:22:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l couldn't take it anymore and l...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm the one who did something unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go back to how we were anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.06,0:22:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W... Who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to go back to how we were!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just want to be friends with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:23:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just want to run with you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erika... You're such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akino!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akino...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, let go! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erika... Erika...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.18,0:24:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akino...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.25,0:24:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, let's go together...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.95,0:24:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.09,0:24:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.39,0:24:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.79,0:24:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.10,0:24:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to atone for our sins here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.20,0:24:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.07,0:24:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... Akino...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.47,0:24:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.61,0:24:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows when it'll be over...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.81,0:24:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to continue to suffer until our sins have been atoned, Erika.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.95,0:24:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.15,0:24:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''We will fall with the others. No one is good here. Not one person...''
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.26,0:25:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''This moment, when humans are engulfed by their evil doings...''
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.37,0:26:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Erika. My body is so light here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.44,0:26:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, everyone's waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.22,0:27:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erika! Erika! Erika! Erika!
